General Manager - Integrated Advertising Agency - Dubai
Tax Free Competitive Package
Shortlist
Add to shortlist
Our client is leading Dubai based Integrated Agency. Part of a Globally famous network, you will be instrumental in leading the agency to new and exciting heights.
The agency is approx 45+ people and growing, you should have experience of running agencies of this size and be a firm believer in producing exciting and award winning creative work.
We need a strong leader with a background of leadership success. You should also have worked for a globally respected brand/agency.
The position is Dubai based and is a very exciting opportunity for someone who is looking for an international role.
Tax Free package
